{"tid":2206357,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"【達觀心戰】權力核心大腦閉塞 - 何安達","createTime":"2020-09-17T12:13:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-17T12:13:37.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e729f963f44ad6d9a67e6c79e0748de4c63a1c2d","tid":2206357,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T12:13:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200917/W5O7BBPHENHGTIVBJ52VLYXL6M/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200917%2FW5O7BBPHENHGTIVBJ52VLYXL6M%2F&d=sV3HumZuViP2rFeoL7TNOOrkGmmZttFFipzpmUasbQ8%3D&h=ab61285c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200917%2FW5O7BBPHENHGTIVBJ52VLYXL6M%2F&h=805e5b16\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200917/W5O7BBPHENHGTIVBJ52VLYXL6M/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n【達觀心戰】權力核心大腦閉塞 - 何安達<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/SBHRVf05Sfu1WYzc2L3xoffIQjE=/6720x4480/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/GNRSRIQI4VAU7JGAMIJLE6P3N4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FSBHRVf05Sfu1WYzc2L3xoffIQjE%3D%2F6720x4480%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FGNRSRIQI4VAU7JGAMIJLE6P3N4.jpg&h=65ab0317&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■林鄭月娥<br />\n<br />\n日前美國雜誌《The Atlantic》引述三名消息人士，指去年721林鄭與數名心腹在禮賓府觀看電視直播。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n報道用了285字便折射出港府最高層的離地程度，當。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n當晚事態嚴峻，警總指揮中心卻無向更高層滙報。負責行政長官保安的小隊，24小時都有人近距離守在特首附近。如果特首沒有接聽電話，或者沒有閱讀手機上的重要訊息，只要聯絡副官或者在禮賓府當值的G4警員，隨時可以透過他們即時直接把消息轉達。就算警察無意識或者根本不願意即時上報，其他局長、秘書長的助理也應該即時有所動作。不過房間以外的相關人事，都止於發WhatsApp訊息，而再沒有多走一步。<br />\n<br />\n由此可見，政府高層並沒有勇於敲老闆門的文化。更嚴重的是，在小圈子最終收到訊息後，根本沒有即時發出有助局勢發展的指示或回應。在在反映出權力核心大腦閉塞。<br />\n<br />\n何安達<br />\n<br />\nhoontat@yahoo.com"}]}